    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SURVIVE IN THE DARKNESS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It Consumes is an FPS survivors game that plays like a combination of Devil Daggers and Vampire Survivors, but with an additional twist: to see you must use your <i>pulse</i> to temporarily reveal your surroundings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371060/extras/2486ae0fe6c56ecbed311f73cbd5a2a7.poster.avif?t=1770942076\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371060/extras/2486ae0fe6c56ecbed311f73cbd5a2a7.webm?t=1770942076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371060/extras/2486ae0fe6c56ecbed311f73cbd5a2a7.mp4?t=1770942076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EVERY RUN IS UNIQUE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain new abilities, upgrade your firepower and mobility, and become an unstoppable demon slaying machine. Different upgrades reward different styles of play, so there are always new strategies to try out when you start a new run. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371060/extras/bb701531a3e5945cbc840fbe42ff670a.poster.avif?t=1770942076\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371060/extras/bb701531a3e5945cbc840fbe42ff670a.webm?t=1770942076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371060/extras/bb701531a3e5945cbc840fbe42ff670a.mp4?t=1770942076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Customize your build.</u></strong> Equip your preferred weapons and abilities, and unlock dozens of perks. Mix and match them to create your perfect playstyle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Difficulty modifier system</u></strong><u>.</u> Unlock  modifiers that add new challenge and change the way you play. Increase the challenge by enabling more modifiers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Meaningful rewards.</u></strong> Completing runs at higher difficulties unlocks powerful special abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Custom games</strong></u><strong>.</strong> Break the game entirely by designing your own custom game mode. Adjust almost any value (such as damage, ammo capacity, movement speed, etc.), toggle on or off any combination of player upgrades, and design your own enemy waves.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >   </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371060/extras/2c8588eddf1ba41466343905b64b8b5d.poster.avif?t=1770942076\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371060/extras/2c8588eddf1ba41466343905b64b8b5d.webm?t=1770942076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2371060/extras/2c8588eddf1ba41466343905b64b8b5d.mp4?t=1770942076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
